    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/c955487e9e0b908be29d64eaf899197c.poster.avif?t=1646330757\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/c955487e9e0b908be29d64eaf899197c.webm?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/c955487e9e0b908be29d64eaf899197c.mp4?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>选择3名冒险者组建成你的团队,探索并把地牢清空! 用冒险者的技能,根据颜色匹配破坏每回合的方块,并在仅有的机会下尝试攻击地牢的首领.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/cf91bd995c9dad665bcc279aaffd8687.poster.avif?t=1646330757\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/cf91bd995c9dad665bcc279aaffd8687.webm?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/cf91bd995c9dad665bcc279aaffd8687.mp4?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每个冒险者都有自己的技能形状来破坏方,当颜色匹配时更会获得额外的伤害.你可以在冒险者技能上装备符文使其更强大,并在您感到危险时使用物品排除危机吧.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/8f6efe82b2a9ebbacfa0b3a385f5c7a1.poster.avif?t=1646330757\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/8f6efe82b2a9ebbacfa0b3a385f5c7a1.webm?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/8f6efe82b2a9ebbacfa0b3a385f5c7a1.mp4?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>颜色与形状匹配的地牢冒险等着你！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/a9a17693ba1e634c0d919403a5a3a440.poster.avif?t=1646330757\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/a9a17693ba1e634c0d919403a5a3a440.webm?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/a9a17693ba1e634c0d919403a5a3a440.mp4?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特征</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>颜色配对<br></li><li>形状配对<br></li><li>回合制游戏<br></li><li>每次地牢之旅都有10个不同的首领需要击败<br></li><li>50个首领有自己独特的被动技能来对付你的冒险团<br></li><li>从9个职业里组建你的冒险团<br></li><li>14种不同的符文让您装备在技能<br></li><li>13种不同的物品来解决你的困境</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/c33392d28b270031457cb077bccb295a.poster.avif?t=1646330757\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/c33392d28b270031457cb077bccb295a.webm?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815050/extras/c33392d28b270031457cb077bccb295a.mp4?t=1646330757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
